org.synchronoss.cpo

Interface CpoWhere

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BindableCpoWhere, JdbcCpoWhere

    public interface CpoWhere
    CpoWhere is an interface for specifying the where clause to filter objects that are returned from the Datasource.
    Author:
    david berry
